column5: KL as many know if the dollar weaken a bit it could really set this off Gold looking better with all the geopolitical noise

KL I feel like another leg up Friday after the market absorbs these past solid days I believe that things really havent changed that much geopolitically China will continue to be difficult EU will have economic travails as it digests Brexit as a forgone conclusion with perhaps a couple of other countries coming forward to limit EUs control Italyetc I believe rate cut will also be accepted as an absolute in second half of the year and goodsservices costing more for various reasons Well Im shooting for 42 as PT by the 4th of July Kind of crazy
